# O(n2)

# 선택정렬 (selection sort)

  • worst case space complexity : O(n) total, O(1) auxiliary
  • youtube - Minsuk Heo (opens new window)
  • github code (java) (opens new window)

# 삽입정렬 (insertion sort)

  • space complexity : O(1)
  • youtube - Minsuk Heo (opens new window)
  • github code (java) (opens new window)

# O(n logn)

# 병합 정렬 (merge sort)

  • space complexity : O(n)
  • youtube - Minsuk Heo (opens new window)
  • github code (java) (opens new window)

# 퀵 정렬 (quick sort)

  • worst case time complexity : O(n2)

  • youtube - Minsuk Heo (opens new window)
